\c 22
\s Ukukhala okulosizi. Ukudumisa iN\nd kosi\nd*
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Ngempala yokusa. Isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 Nkulunkulu wami, Nkulunkulu wami, ungitshiyeleni\x + Mat. 27.46. Mark. 15.34.\x* na? Ukhatshana lokungisiza, \add l\add*amazwi okubhonga kwami\x + Jobe 3.24. Hlab. 32.3. Hlab. 38.8. Heb. 5.7.\x*?
\v 2 Nkulunkulu wami, ngiyakhala emini, kodwa kawungiphenduli, lebusuku, kodwa kangilakho ukuthula\x + Hlab. 88.1.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa wena ungcwele, ohlezi \add e\add*zibongw\add eni\add* zikaIsrayeli\x + Dute. 10.21.\x*.
\v 4 Obaba bethu bathemba kuwe, bathemba, wasubakhulula.
\v 5 Bakhala kuwe, bakhululwa\x + Hlu. 3.9.\x*; bathembela kuwe, kabayangekanga\x + 22.4. Hlab. 25.2.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa ngingumswenya, kangisuye muntu\x + Jobe 25.6. Isa. 41.14. Mat. 2.23.\x*, ihlazo labantu\x + Hlab. 69.19. 109.25.\x*, ngeyiswa ngabantu\x + Isa. 49.7. 53.3.\x*.
\v 7 Bonke abangibonayo bayangihleka usulu\x + Mat. 27.39. Mark. 15.29.\x*, bakhamisa indebe, banikine ikhanda\x + Hlab. 109.25. Hlab. 44.14. 2 Kho. 19.21.\x*,
\v 8 \add besithi\add*: Wathembela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Mat. 27.43.\x*; kayimkhulule\x + Hlab. 91.14.\x*, imophule, ngoba yathokoza kuye\x + 2 Sam. 15.26.\x*.
