\v 9 Kodwa nguwe owangikhupha esiswini\x + Jobe 38.8.\x*\x + Hlab. 71.6.\x*, wangenza ngathemba \add ngis\add*emabeleni kamama.
\v 10 Ngalahlelwa phezu kwakho kusukela esizalweni\x + Jobe 38.8.\x*; kusukela esiswini sikamama unguNkulunkulu wami\x + Isa. 46.3.\x*.
\v 11 Ungabi khatshana lami, ngoba uhlupho luseduze, ngoba kakho osizayo.
\v 12 Izinkunzi ezinengi zingihanqile, ezilamandla\x + Hlab. 50.13. 68.30.\x* zeBashani\x + Dute. 32.14. Hez. 39.18. Amos 4.1. Jer. 50.19. Mika 7.14.\x* zingizingelezele\x + Hlu. 20.43.\x*.
\v 13 Zangikhamisela umlomo wazo, isilwane esiphangayo lesibhongayo\x + Jobe 16.10. Hlab. 35.21.\x*.
\v 14 Ngithululiwe njengamanzi\x + Lilo 2.11.\x*, lamathambo ami wonke ehlukene; inhliziyo yami\x + Nah. 2.10. Josh. 2.11. Jobe 23.16. Hlab. 104.26.\x* injengengcino\x + Hlab. 68.2.\x*, incibilikile phakathi kwemibilini yami\x + Nah. 2.10. Josh. 2.11. Jobe 23.16. Hlab. 104.26.\x*.
\v 15 Amandla ami omile njengodengezi\x + Zaga 17.22.\x*, lolimi lwami lunamathele emihlathini yami\x + Lilo 4.4. Joha. 19.28.\x*; ungibeke ethulini lokufa.
\v 16 Ngoba izinja zingigombolozele\x + 22.20. Fil. 3.2. Isam. 22.15.\x*; inhlangano yababi ingihanqile\x + Hlab. 88.17.\x*; izandla zami lenyawo zami bazibhobozile\x + Mat. 27.35. Mark. 15.24. Luka 23.33. 24.40. Joha. 19.23,37. 20.25.\x*.
\v 17 Ngingabala wonke amathambo ami; bona bayakhangela bayangijolozela\x + Luka 23.35.\x*.
\v 18 Babelana izigqoko zami, benza inkatho yokuphosa ngezembatho zami\x + Mat. 27.35. Joha. 19.24. Luka 23.34.\x*.
