\v 19 Kodwa, wena N\nd kosi\nd*, ungabi khatshana; mandla ami, phangisa ukungisiza\x + 22.11. Hlab. 35.22.\x*.
\v 20 Khulula umphefumulo wami kuyo inkemba, wona wodwa owami emandleni enja\x + 22.16.\x*.
\v 21 Ngisindisa emlonyeni wesilwane\x + 2 Tim. 4.17.\x*; ngoba empondweni zezinyathi\x + Nani 23.22.\x* ungiphendule\x + 22.2.\x*.
