\v 22 Ngizalandisa ibizo lakho\x + 22.25. Hlab. 102.21. Heb. 2.12. Joha. 17.6.\x* kubafowethu\x + Mat. 28.10.\x*, phakathi kwebandla ngizakudumisa.
\v 23 Lina elesaba iN\nd kosi\nd*, idumiseni\x + Hlab. 135.20.\x*; lonke nzalo kaJakobe, ihlonipheni; liyesabe, lonke nzalo kaIsrayeli\x + Hlab. 50.15,23.\x*.
\v 24 Ngoba kayidelelanga kayinengwanga yinhlupheko yohluphekayo; njalo kayimfihlelanga ubuso bayo; kodwa lapho ekhala kuyo, yezwa\x + Heb. 5.7.\x*.
\v 25 Indumiso yami izakuba ngawe ebandleni elikhulu\x + Hlab. 35.18. 40.9,10. 22.22. Hlab. 26.12. 107.32. 109.30. 111.1.\x*; ngizakhokha izifungo zami phambi kwabayesabayo\x + Hlab. 50.14. 66.13. 76.11. 116.14,18. Jona 2.9. Nani 30.2.\x*.
\v 26 Abamnene bazakudla basuthe; bazayidumisa iN\nd kosi\nd* labo abayidingayo\x + Isa. 65.13.\x*. Inhliziyo yenu\x + Hlab. 69.32.\x* izaphila kuze kube phakade\x + Joha. 6.51.\x*.
\v 27 Imikhawulo yonke yomhlaba izakhumbula, iphendukele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Hlab. 2.8. 59.13. 67.7. 98.3. Isa. 52.10. Hlab. 48.10. 65.5. 72.11. 86.9. Isa. 49.6.\x*; lezizukulwana zonke zezizwe zizakhonza phambi kwakho\x + Hlab. 96.7. Hlab. 66.4.\x*.
\v 28 Ngoba umbuso ungoweN\nd kosi\nd*, njalo iyabusa phakathi kwezizwe\x + Obad. 21. Hlab. 47.8.\x*.
\v 29 Bonke abakhulupheleyo bomhlaba bazakudla bakhonze\x + Hlab. 45.12. Hlab. 78.31.\x*; bonke abehlela othulini bazakhothama phambi kwayo\x + Hlab. 72.9.\x*, longagcini umphefumulo wakhe uphila.
\v 30 Inzalo izayikhonza; izabalelwa eNkosini kuso isizukulwana\x + Hlab. 87.6.\x*.
\v 31 Bazakuza bamemezele ukulunga kwayo\x + Hlab. 86.9.\x* ebantwini abazazalwa, ukuthi i\add kw\add*enzile\x + Hlab. 78.6. Hlab. 102.18.\x*.